quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,196,mera madadgaar to khuda hi hai jis ne kitaab ( barhaq ) nazil ki. aur naik logon ka wohi Dostdar hai
  7,197,aur jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh nah tumhari hi madad ki taaqat rakhtay hain aur nah khud hi apni madad kar saktay hain
  7,198,aur agar tum un ko seedhay raste ki taraf bulaao to sun nah saken aur tum inhen dekhte ho ke ( bah zahir ) ankhen khole tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain magar ( fi al waqea ) kuch nahi dekhte
  7,199,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) Afoo ikhtiyar karo aur naik kaam karne ka hukum do aur jahilon se kinara karlo
  7,200,aur agar shetan ki taraf se tumahray dil mein kisi terhan ka waswasa peda ho to khuda se panah mango. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
  7,201,jo log parhaizgaar hain jab un ko shetan ki taraf se koi waswasa peda hota hai to choank parte hain aur ( dil ki ankhen khol kar ) dekhnay lagtay hain
  7,202,aur un ( kufar ) ke bhai inhen gumraahi mein kheinchain jatay hain phir ( is mein kisi terhan ki ) kotahi nahi karte
  7,203,aur jab tum un ke paas ( kuch dinon taq ) koi aayat nahi laatay to kehte hain ke tum ne ( apni taraf se ) kyun nahi banali. keh do ke mein to isi ki pairwi karta hon jo mere perwar-digaar ki taraf se mere paas aata hai. yeh quran tumahray perwar-digaar ki janib se Danish -o- basirat aur mominon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  7,204,aur jab quran parha jaye to tavajja se suna karo aur khamosh raha karo taakay tum par rehamkiya jaye
  7,205,aur apne perwar-digaar ko dil hi dil mein aajzi aur khauf se aur pust aawaz se subah vsham yaad karte raho aur ( dekhna ) ghaafil nah hona
  7,206,jo log tumahray perwar-digaar ke paas hain woh is ki ibadat se gardan kashi nahi karte aur is pak zaat ko yaad karte aur is ke agay sjday karte rehtay hain
